cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement

Interface IEntitlementVisitable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Entitlement, Item, Permission, Resource, Role, User

    public interface IEntitlementVisitable
    Interface that marks implementing classes as able to accept an IEntitlementVisitor for building up a printable product inventory.
    See Also:
    cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement.Service, Entitlement, Role, Permission, User, IEntitlementVisitor
